data.name: lblRules2.Text
data.value:
1. Follow the instructions after you toss
2. The goal between 50 to 100 is reasonable but no restrictions (Maximum goal 100)
3. If either of the dice rolls a one the running score is lost, and the dice automatically pass to the opponent
4. If both of your dices rolls a one, you lose not only the running score but also your cumulative score
5. If your reach the goal you win the game
6. You have to put your name to set the goal
